<div id="page-wrapper" style="margin:0px;">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12">
            <h1 class="page-header">
                <center>
                    <img src="images/banner.png" style="display: block; height: auto; max-width: 100%;" />
                </center>
            </h1>
        </div>
        <!-- /.col-lg-12 -->
    </div>

    <h1>{{title}}</h1>
    <div class="alert alert-success" id="submissionSuccess" role="alert" style="display:none">Thank you for providing feedback.
        <br/>
        <br/>Your responses are important and will be reviewed.
        <br/>A shortlist of common wishlist requests will be considered according to their frequency
        <br/>
    </div>
    <div class="row" id="externalcloudFeedback">
        <div class="panel-group">
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <span class="fa fa-align-left fa-cloud">
                        </span>Feedback</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <div class="form-area col-md-8 col-md-offset-2 col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1 col-xs-12">
                        <form role="form">
                            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center;">What's on your mind?</h3>
                            <h4 style="margin-bottom: 25px; text-align: center;" id="motd"></h4>
                            <div class="col-sm-12" style="padding-top:25px;padding-bottom:10px;">
                                <p>All requests are currently being raised as Innovation requests</p>
                                <p>You need to already have an MSDN subscription to use this service. If you do not you should
                                    request one by sending a mail
                                    <a href="mailto:anzsoftwarelicensing@anz.com?subject=New%20MSDN%20Subscription&body=Please%20create%20a%20new%20subscription%0D%0AName:%0D%0ALANID:%0D%0ABSB/CC:%0D%0ACountry:%0D%0A%0D%0ASubscription%20Option:%0D%0A[Choose%20One%20of%20the%20following]:%0D%0AVisual%20Studio%20Pro%20(Visual%20Studio%20test%20%26%20dev%20tools%20using%20%20SQL%20%26%20Windows%0D%0AVisual%20Studio%20Enterprise%20(Visual%20Studio%20test%20%26%20dev%20tools%20using%20Microsoft%27s%20complete%20product%20set)%0D%0AMSDN%20Platforms%20(access%20to%20the%20complete%20Microsoft%20product%20set%20for%20the%20non-prod%20environment,%20perfect%20for%20people%20not%20requiring%20the%20test%20%26%20dev%20tools%20but%20just%20want%20to%20use%20MSFT%20software%20in%20the%20non-prod%20environment)                                  
                                                    ">here</a>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group col-sm-6 has-feedback">
                                <div class="input-group has-feedback">
                                    <span class="input-group-addon">Which Initiative did you work on?
                                        <span class="fa fa-info-circle" data-toggle="tooltip"
                                            title="" data-original-title="If you haven't yet raised a request simply leave this blank"></span>
                                    </span>
                                    <input type="text" class="form-control" id="initiativename">
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group col-sm-6 has-feedback">
                                <div class="input-group has-feedback">
                                    <span class="input-group-addon">How would you rate your experience?
                                        <span class="fa fa-info-circle" data-toggle="tooltip" title="" data-original-title="chose a rating where 10 is the highest rating"></span>
                                    </span>
                                    <input type="number" value="5" min="1" max="10" class="form-control" id="costcentre">
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="form-group col-sm-6">
                                <label class="col-sm-12">What did you like?
                                    <span class="fa fa-info-circle" data-toggle="tooltip" title="" data-original-title="What worked well to make your experience better?"></span>
                                </label>
                                <textarea class="form-control" type="textarea" id="readers" maxlength="140" rows="6"></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group col-sm-6">
                                <label class="col-sm-12">What didn't you like?
                                    <span class="fa fa-info-circle" data-toggle="tooltip" title="" data-original-title="What could have been done better?"></span>
                                </label>
                                <textarea class="form-control" type="textarea" id="contributors" maxlength="140" rows="6"></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group col-sm-12">
                                <label class="col-sm-12">Do you have any suggestions  ?
                                    <span class="fa fa-info-circle" data-toggle="tooltip" title="" data-original-title="What would you like to see in future releases?"></span>
                                </label>
                                <textarea class="form-control" type="textarea" id="assistanceRequestedNotes" maxlength="140" rows="3"></textarea>
                            </div>
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
                                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-lg btn-block span6" id="giveFeedback">Submit Request</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>